data.name: label2.Text
data.value: This application will swap around original files with the modded files (and keep the originals in a backup folder.) When you want to add more mods, or if the Blade and Soul launcher starts checking for files, you must cancel it! Then run this app and press the Undo button. Then add your new mods, or let the launcher check for files.

data.name: label5.Text
data.value: Please use the below button to point this app to your Blade and Soul folder. Make sure you do not place this application within the Blade and Soul install folder. If you want to use the "Launch NCSoft Launcher" button as well, you can use the "Set NCSoft Folder" button to enable it.
